or: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Considers <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/opener\">window.opener</a></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>49.0 (49)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">Secure contexts</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"window.isSecureContext是一个判断上下文是否能够使用安全上下文的特征的只读属性。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.isSecureContext","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.isSecureContext","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/issecurecontext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/issecurecontext/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":